bug.author: advaitjain
bug.summary: Reproduce internal CI errors via TF Lite Micro Makefile
bug.description:
<denchmark-link:https://github.com/orgs/tensorflow/teams/micro>@tensorflow/micro</denchmark-link>
See <denchmark-link:https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/pull/42452#issuecomment-689199971>this comment</denchmark-link> for an internal error, due to -Wswitch that we could not reproduce via the TFLM Makefile. The underlying issue there was a missing -Wswitch in the makefile and an inability to build without -DTF_LITE_STATIC_MEMORY.
